01:25.486 --> 01:30.189
<i>Okay, good, thank you.
And don't forget your, um, security code.</i>

02:12.233 --> 02:13.765
Should we start?
I think we should start.

02:13.767 --> 02:15.234
Yeah, who is that guy?

02:15.236 --> 02:16.602
I thought we were getting
a bagpipe player

02:16.604 --> 02:18.237
I thought... but he's
playing a flute.

02:18.239 --> 02:19.771
I mean, that's not
even a real flute,

02:19.773 --> 02:21.440
That's like a frickin'
Native American thing.

02:21.442 --> 02:23.342
Who is this guy?
Do you know him?

02:23.344 --> 02:25.277
That's Tom Running-cloud.
I went to high school with him.

02:25.279 --> 02:26.879
